calling convention:
- fuck 32-bit chuds
- rax for syscall NR and return
- RDI -> 0
- RSI -> 1
- RDX -> 2
- R10 -> 3
- R8  -> 4
- R9  -> 5
- more -> stack


name | desc | RAX | RDI | RSI | RDX | R10 | R8  | R9  | more?
-----|------|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-------
read | buh  | 0   | file desc | buf* | size|
write | buh | 0x01| file desc | buf* | size
